> currently curve only supports swapping between tokens of (relatively) equal value.
@Magnus i know, but the reason why is because liquidity providing is super risky for anything that's crypto because of very rapid price movements. Curve is the low risk LP choice because uniswap/balancer are very high risk for LPs

